latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey everyone! Here’s my latest video. A tribute to the ever amazing @britneyspears Our team has put in a lot of efforts to get this output and I’d sincerely like to thank each and everyone who brought this project to life! Thank you @sandip.solleti & Nirvana Photography for your faith in me and for the wonderful output! Thank you to Renu & the tech team involved. Thank you to @styliciousbysam & @gulzarrwalaani for getting onboard and creating such fabulous looks for me! The place we shot at was a super beautiful location @studiorangasthalam Also, a big thank you to all my family, friends and admirers for always showering me with your love and support and last but not the least I’d like to thank myself for being able to test new waters! latestPosts.caption:
On this special day, I want to honor the woman who has shaped my world with love, wisdom and grace. To the one who has sacrificed some moments of happiness in her life so that I could have them in my own life. You are a blessing to me, and I admire you and love you more than words can say. May the Lord let you enjoy his light and kindness everyday; may his blessings and love overflow your life.

May God give you good health, peace, love, joy, prosperity, immense wealth and divine favour now and in the years to come. May the fruits and the gifts of the Holy Spirit work completely in and through your life. May you be an incredible blessing to every person you meet and pray for. May the Lord continue to divinely protect you from seen and unseen forces. I decree and declare every area of your life be victorious! In Jesus mighty name I ask and pray. Thank you Lord, for answering my prayer in advance. Amen 

You are my biggest inspiration always! Happy Birthday to my mumma, my QUEEN 👸🏽
